column2: SELECT my.id, my.ra_s, my.dec_s, my.bmag, my.bvcolour, my.z_s, match.distance, u, g, r, i, z, dered_u, dered_g, dered_r, dered_i, dered_z into mydb.s2#_sdss_phot from MyDb.s2# AS my CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEQ (my.ra_s, my.dec_s, #) AS match JOIN PhotoPrimary AS p ON p.ObjID = match.ObjID
